  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">ISK revision av IBON 2022</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Internal Controll Review ISK of IBON 2022</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">During the current project period, Sida discovered that the organization passed on funds incorrectly (the same payment twice) and that the audit for 2019 had to be redone. This indicates that there could be weaknesses in the organization&apos;s internal governance and control. As Sida in 2022 needs to decide on what the collaboration will look like from 2023, an ISK review needs to be carried out.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Under nuvarande projektperiod uppt&#xE4;ckte Sida att organisationen vidaref&#xF6;rmedlat medel p&#xE5; ett felaktigt s&#xE4;tt (samma utbetalning tv&#xE5; g&#xE5;nger) samt att revisionen f&#xF6;r &#xE5;r 2019 fick g&#xF6;ras om. Detta indikerar att det skulle kunna finnas svagheter i organisationens interna styrning och kontroll. D&#xE5; Sida under 2022 beh&#xF6;ver besluta om hur samarbetet ska se ut fr&#xE5;n och med 2023 beh&#xF6;ver en ISK-granskning genomf&#xF6;ras.</narrative>
  </description>
